The Todo Academy, the setting for the broadcast series Tenjho Tenge (2004), was created to revive Tokugawa era martial arts: it's a high school of brawling thugs, ruled by a student "executive council."     After Maya's dismissal from school, Souichiro and Bob also submit their resignation from school in protest.
 Meanwhile, Aya disappears with Shin's cursed sword, the Choukto-reiki. With Dragon's Eye growing hold over Aya along with Shin's sword, both Maya and Mitsuomi fear that history will repeat itself and Aya will continue the path of blood that her older brother started in the past.
